snippet.title: Southfield Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST SOUTHFIELD ➤ https://bit.ly/FindSouthfield

Get ready to explore the wild and ever-changing world of Southfield, grow a harvest of chaotic and unpredictable crops, build your dream farmstead, and experiment with playful machinery. Our physics-based farming game is COMING SOON to Steam early access!

See more ➤ https://southfieldgame.com
